import jax
import jax.numpy as jnp

def generated_fn(x0, x1, x2):
    v0 = jnp.cos(x2)
    v1 = jnp.subtract(v0, x0)
    v2 = jnp.minimum(v1, x1)
    v3 = jnp.multiply(x1, x0)
    v4 = jnp.maximum(v3, v2)
    v5 = jnp.sin(v0)
    v6 = jnp.add(v5, x0)
